ext":"Aliens land and the humans won’t change"},{"s":38.2,"e":40.7,"text":"Everybody online, everybody in pain"},{"s":40.66,"e":43.28,"text":"Everybody got a screen, nobody got a name"},{"s":43.28,"e":45.2,"text":"You been under that stone too long"},{"s":45.2,"e":47.6,"text":"Whole earth crying, hear that song"},{"s":47.6,"e":50.38,"text":"We need hands, we need heart, we need everybody strong"},{"s":50.38,"e":52.88,"text":"If you got wisdom, bring it along"},{"s":52.88,"e":55.32,"text":"Little green friend with the big black eyes"},{"s":55.58,"e":57.78,"text":"You seen ten moons and a thousand skies"},{"s":57.78,"e":60.46,"text":"But have you seen love when a poor man rise?"},{"s":60.68,"e":62.96,"text":"Have you seen truth make a dead soul fly?"},{"s":63.28,"e":64.18,"text":"Come out the cave"},{"s":64.42,"e":65.46,"text":"Come out the cold"},{"s":65.62,"e":66.64,"text":"Bring what you know"},{"s":66.86,"e":67.82,"text":"Heal what we broke"},{"s":67.82,"e":70.32,"text":"If you been sleeping under a rock"},{"s":70.44,"e":72.8,"text":"Come see the stars, come feel the shock"},{"s":72.8,"e":75.36,"text":"The world is broken, but it ain’t done"},{"s":75.58,"e":77.88,"text":"Wake up, wake up, here comes the sun"},{"s":77.88,"e":80.42,"text":"If you came down from another sky"},{"s":80.54,"e":82.96,"text":"Don’t hide your heart, don’t pass us by"},{"s":82.94,"e":85.44,"text":"We need your light, we need your spark"},{"s":85.52,"e":88.14,"text":"Come help us shine through the dark"},{"s":88.08,"e":90.58,"text":"This for the ones who been late to the news"},{"s":90.58,"e":93.12,"text":"Earth got problems, but we still got moves"},{"s":93.12,"e":95.72,"text":"Still got children with impossible dreams"},{"s":95.72,"e":98.32,"text":"Still got rivers, still got trees"},{"s":98.32,"e":100.72,"text":"Still got hunger we can end real fast"},{"s":100.72,"e":103.32,"text":"Still got wounds from a violent past"},{"s":103.32,"e":105.94,"text":"Still got people who forgot how to ask"},{"s":105.94,"e":108.11,"text":"Still got love that can outlast ash"},{"s":108.58,"e":110.92,"text":"So if you’re human, alien, angel, or odd"},{"s":110.92,"e":113.13,"text":"Step in the light, put your work before God"},{"s":113.5,"e":116,"text":"No more hiding, no more playing detached"},{"s":116,"e":118.6,"text":"Wake up now, whole world need patched"},{"s":118.6,"e":121.1,"text":"Under the rock, we were waiting"},{"s":121.1,"e":123.58,"text":"Out in the dark, hearts breaking"},{"s":123.58,"e":126.04,"text":"Up in the stars, lights shaking"},{"s":126.3,"e":128.56,"text":"Now we rise, no more faking"},{"s":128.56,"e":131,"text":"If you been sleeping under a rock"},{"s":131,"e":133.48,"text":"Come see the stars, come feel the shock"},{"s":133.42,"e":135.96,"text":"The world is broken, but it ain’t done"},{"s":135.96,"e":138.52,"text":"Wake up, wake up, here comes the sun"},{"s":138.52,"e":141.02,"text":"If you came down from another sky"},{"s":141.1,"e":143.58,"text":"Don’t hide your heart, don’t pass us by"},{"s":143.58,"e":146.1,"text":"We need your light, we need your spark"},{"s":146.16,"e":148.9,"text":"Come help us shine through the dark"},{"s":150.4,"e":152.48,"text":"Aliens, humans"},{"s":152.64,"e":154.82,"text":"Lost ones, strange ones"},{"s":154.82,"e":157.22,"text":"Rock sleepers, star keepers"},{"s":157.46,"e":158.42,"text":"Wake up"},{"s":158.58,"e":159.82,"text":"We got work to do."}],"duration":160,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.290Z","stats":{"whisperWords":454,"polishedWords":454,"matched":443,"matchRate":0.976}}